# Citation Export Normalizer Prototype

This prototype demonstrates the core backend pipeline for
cleaning citation exports from Scopus / Web of Science.

Pipeline:

RIS Export
↓
Parser
↓
Structured JSON
↓
Deduplication (DOI + title similarity)
↓
Metadata enrichment (CrossRef API)
↓
Normalized citation dataset

Features demonstrated:

✔ RIS parsing
✔ DOI-based deduplication
✔ Title similarity matching
✔ CrossRef metadata enrichment
✔ Error handling for API failures

Example Output

Input records: 1
After dedupe: 1
Normalized dataset saved.